&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>Mar 26, &lt;span class="m">2024&lt;/span> - 15:07:15 &lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>CET&lt;span class="o">)]&lt;/span> exegol-htb Headless &lt;span class="c1"># pwncat-cs -lp 9001&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>15:07:21&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span> Welcome to pwncat 🐈! __main__.py:164
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>15:07:25&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span> received connection from 10.10.11.8:42146 bind.py:84
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>15:07:26&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span> 0.0.0.0:9001: upgrading from /usr/bin/dash to /usr/bin/bash manager.py:957
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>15:07:27&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span> 10.10.11.8:42146: registered new host w/ db manager.py:957
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">local&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> pwncat:
